====================================================================
MAP INFO
====================================================================

Map                   : gg_quakev2
Game                  : Counter-Strike: Source
Game type             : Gun Game
Recommmended Players  : 10-20
Description           : A small map that is textured with reworked, 
                        high-quality quake 1 textures.  Basically 
                        a big square with a platform in middle, a 
                        path beneath it, and staircases on either
                        side going up to the platform.

====================================================================
INSTALLATION
====================================================================

Place gg_quakev2 in your Steam\SteamApps\youremailaddress\
counter-strike source\cstrike\maps folder.

====================================================================
CONTACT
====================================================================

Author                : Fallows
Contact               : foullows@gmail.com
